<h3>Show Notes:</h3>

<p>
	In this episode, Dan and Bekah welcome Tori to talk about her journey through
	the interview process that included about 53 interviews, 430 applications, and
	a pandemic offer that ultimately led to her being ghosted by the company. She
	gives her tips and tricks, including recognizing that interviews are a two-way
	street; you should also be interviewing the companies that are interviewing
	you. She talks about the problems of technical interviewing, how she's hopeful
	that the industry can make changes, and how the job she ultimately landed has
	been a great experience, starting with the interview.
</p>

